*CHARMM minimization *
BOMB -4
OPEN READ UNIT 12 CARD NAME "amino.rtf"
READ RTF UNIT 12 CARD
CLOSE UNIT 12
OPEN READ UNIT 13 CARD NAME "param.prm"
READ PARAMETERS UNIT 13 CARD
CLOSE UNIT 13

OPEN READ UNIT 14 CARD NAME "1BBB.pdb1"
READ SEQUENCE PDB UNIT 14
GENERATE 1BBB SETUP
REWIND UNIT 14
READ COORDINATES PDB UNIT 14
CLOSE UNIT 14

IC FILL PRESERVE
IC PARAMETERS
IC BUILD
HBUILD

NBONDS VSHIFT RDIE EPS 4. CUTNB 15.0
CONS FIX SELE (TYPE CA .OR. TYPE N .OR. TYPE C .OR. TYPE O) END

SET 1 0
LABEL BEGIN
MINIMIZE ABNR NSTEP 10 NPRINT 10 TOLENG 0.0001 TOLGRD 0.0001
INCREMENT 1 BY 1
IF 1 GT 9 GOTO FINISH
GOTO BEGIN
LABEL FINISH

OPEN UNIT 21 NAME "1lig.min" WRITE FORM
WRITE TITLE UNIT 21
*MM ?BOND ?DIHE ?ANGL ?IMPR ?VDW ?ELEC ?ENER
WRITE COOR PDB UNIT 21
